  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook Canadian Bacon in a pan until browned, then set aside.",
    "In the same pan, add Xtra Virgin Olive Oil and sauté the chopped Onion, Mushroom, Carrot, and Celery until tender.",
    "Add the cooked Canadian Bacon, Lentil, diced Tomato, Salt, and Black Pepper to the pan and stir to combine.",
